high_descs: Go forward and face the counter with the microwave on it.
Pick the apple up from the left of microwave.
Go to the right and face the fridge.
Put the apple in the fridge and shut the door and then open the door and pick the apple back up.
Turn around and face the red trash can next to the counter.
Put the apple in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled apple in the trash can.

high_descs: Face the counter with the microwave in front of you.
Take the apple next to the microwave in front of you.
Turn right and face the fridge to your left.
Place the apple in the fridge in front of you and take it out.
Turn around and face the red trash can in front of you.
Place the apple in the red trash can in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold apple in a trash can.

high_descs: go to corner counter to left of microwave
pick up red apple to the left of microwave
go to refrigerator to the right
open refrigerator, put apple on top shelf, close refrigerator, open refrigerator, pick up apple, close refrigerator
turn around, go to red bin in between table and counter
anns.task_desc: place chilled red apple in red bin
